        <div class="cover-title">10 AI Blog Writers for SEO <span style="opacity:0.6">→</span> Ranked</div>
        <div class="cover-sub">SERP scoring · NLP · Briefs · Publishing · 90-day traffic</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

