    <div class="post-grid">
      <article class="post-content">
        <p class="lede-p">Most AI writers are generic. "AI writers for SEO" are purpose-built — every output is scored against the live top 10 SERPs and tuned for entity coverage, heading depth, and word count. <strong>The difference between a $20 generic writer and an $89 SEO writer shows up in the 90-day rank report.</strong> We tested 10 SEO writers over 90 days on the same domain, same keywords, same target word count.</p>

        <p>The headline: SERP-scoring is now table stakes. The differentiator is whether the writer also closes the loop with publishing, internal linking, and schema. Three tools in this list ship that whole pipeline. The rest leave it to you.</p>

