          <li><strong>Calendar</strong> — 24 articles per writer, 90-day window</li>
          <li><strong>Scoring</strong> — 6 blind reviewers rated drafts; rank movement tracked in SE Ranking</li>
          <li><strong>Metrics</strong> — SERP-score accuracy, output quality, time-to-publish, rank lift</li>
          <li><strong>Total budget</strong> — $4,200 across all 10 subscriptions</li>
        </ul>

